('banana_chips_saging_chips_guamanian', 'Banana Chips (Saging Chips)', 480, 2.5, 64.0, 25.0, 4.0, 30.0, 30, NULL, 'research', ARRAY['banana chips (saging chips)', 'fried banana chips', 'saging crisps', 'sweet banana crisps'], 'snack', NULL, 1, 'GU', 'Thinly sliced bananas deep-fried and coated in sugar or salt; a Filipino-origin snack chip widely sold in Guam''s convenience stores and markets, made from locally grown saba or latundan banana varieties.', TRUE),
