('chocolate_bibingka_chocolate_rice_cake_guamanian', 'Chocolate Bibingka (Chocolate Rice Cake)', 315, 5.5, 48.0, 12.0, 1.0, 26.0, 100, 80, 'research', ARRAY['chocolate bibingka (chocolate rice cake)', 'chocolate rice cake', 'cocoa bibingka', 'choco bibingka guam'], 'dessert', NULL, 1, 'GU', 'A modern CHamoru-Filipino fusion baked rice cake made with coconut milk and chocolate; a creative adaptation of the classic bibingka that incorporates cocoa for a richer flavor, popular at Guam''s contemporary bakeries.', TRUE),
